text.tspan: mizmo posted to the hubs-devel mailing list.

flowRoot.flowPara: This may be the first post to the list :)
I just wanted to send a note out that I triaged through the open tickets and added a 'ui spec' tag to all tickets that are actually UI specs and not bugs or development tasks. Hope that was helpful.

Another thing I did was add a 'needs mockup' tag to any issues that were clearly in need of a mockup (or mockup updates.) If you're working on a ticket and need some design / mockup help, be sure to add this tag. :)

"the grey is matched to the gray used on arm.fpo, but i do agree in this context it looks a little too washed out / inactive. i think it might be better to match the gray to the same as used in the 'ask fedora' logotype so it's clear it's not inactive. i will put the new artwork together for this."
